// I chose TryUnconstrainedThenConstrained to balance between exploring new possibilities and adhering to strict structural requirements.
// This approach allows the model to generate unconstrained content initially, then refine it with constraints.
// The interval N=5 strikes a good balance between exploration and adherence.
// CSD_RATIONALE_END
